column5: Just a note to say HI! I am a bass fisherman mostly......although I can hold my own with anything that swims!  Look forward to getting to know the people and the place!  Stinkbait
Welcome to our board Stinky...Couldn't resist
I'm like you in the multiple species...except I can't catch multiple species equally!  Welcome to the board!
Chris !!!  I can't believe you said that............before i did  Wecome to the group Mr. Bait.
Mister...at least you didn't type Master. Lol

Welcome Stinkbait. You will be a great addition to the site.  You can all thank me for having this fine gentleman, and fishing "expert" join our community. Actually, I did a little kijiji deal with Stinkbait and told him about the site. Although, I should have warned him about a few of you  .
Thank you for the welcomes!  Stinkbait
Yes...Thank you! Hope youhave recieved and are happy with the deal!
Welcome...  Lots of bass fisherman here to share stories and techniques with... And pics...  And you also get to see guys like me stumble accidental into big smallies... Lol...
stinkbait...one of my preferred names on the site. I also like General Sherman (can't go wrong with a Simpson's reference). Welcome
